#ROOM
Vnum     27040
Name     &xThe Downs Entrance&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The warm Barrens air is sucked away, replaced by a draft that smells 
of ancient ice and rotting meat. Massive thorns, blackened by 
necromancy, twist around a swirling, frost-covered portal. This 
unholy gateway separates the southern Barrens from the frozen 
stronghold of the Coldbringer.
~
#EXIT
Direction out~
ToRoom    26533
Desc      Return to the southern Barrens.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    27041
Desc      The path leads into the darkness.~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     27041
Name     &xThe Withered Path&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The tunnel walls are lined with the tattered remains of quilboar 
banners. The ground is littered with bleached bones that crunch 
beneath your feet. A low, constant moaning echoes from the north, 
carried on a freezing wind.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    27040
Desc      The entrance portal.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    27042
Desc      The path continues.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 27001 10 27041
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     27042
Name     &xThe Withered Path - Bend&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The tunnel turns sharply. To the east, a narrow fissure in the 
wall leads to a dark, web-choked passage. The main path continues 
north, toward a large, shadowy chamber.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    27041
Desc      The entry path.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    27046
Desc      The entrance to the Spiral.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    27043
Desc      The path to the central plaza.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 27014 10 27042
Reset O 0 27029 10 27042
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     27043
Name     &xEntry to the Bone-Strewn Plaza&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The ceiling rises into a vaulted dome. Massive piles of skulls 
are arranged in the corners of the room, their hollow sockets 
glowing with a dim, purple light.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    27042
Desc      The withered path.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    27044
Desc      The central plaza.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 27002 10 27043
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     27044
Name     &xThe Bone-Strewn Plaza - South&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This wide-open space was once a place of gathering for the 
tribe, but it is now a harvesting ground for the Scourge. 
Zombies shuffle aimlessly between piles of debris.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    27051
Desc      The path to the Cathedral.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    27043
Desc      The entry hall.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    27045
Desc      A small side chamber.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 27001 10 27044
Reset O 0 27032 10 27044
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     27045
Name     &xSide Chamber of Decay&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This room is used for the disposal of "failed" experiments. The 
stench of rot is nearly physical here.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    27044
Desc      Return to the plaza.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 27010 10 27045
Reset O 0 27031 5 27045
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     27046
Name     &cThe Spiral - Webbed Entrance&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Thick, iron-strong webbing covers the walls and ceiling. The 
air is stagnant and smells of old venom. Tiny shadows skitter 
just beyond the reach of your light.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    27042
Desc      Return to the main path.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    27047
Desc      The spiral corridor.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 27016 10 27046
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     27047
Name     &cThe Spiral - Corridor&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The passage begins to curve downward, looping toward the center 
of the spider wing. Several large, silk-wrapped cocoons hang from 
the ceiling, some of them still twitching.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    27046
Desc      The entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    27048
Desc      A side burrow.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    27049
Desc      The approach to the lair.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 27016 10 27047
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     27048
Name     &cThe Spiral - Side Burrow&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This small burrow is filled with the discarded husks of giant 
insects and small beasts.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    27047
Desc      The corridor.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 27013 10 27048
Reset O 0 27035 1 27048
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     27049
Name     &cThe Spiral - Lair Approach&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The webbing becomes so thick that it forms a natural carpet 
on the floor. The sound of thousands of tiny legs scuttling 
over stone is deafening.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    27047
Desc      The corridor.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    27050
Desc      Tuten'kash's Lair.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 27016 10 27049
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     27050
Name     &cTuten'kash's Webbed Lair&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This massive cavern is a nightmare of silk and shadow. Tuten'kash 
