Reset M 0 27008 10 27051
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     27052
Name     &rThe Bone Cathedral - Nave&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Rows of stone pews are arranged facing the northern altar. 
Undead acolytes stand in the aisles, their voices joined in 
