Reset M 0 27000 10 27052
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     27053
Name     &rThe Bone Cathedral - Transept&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A side wing of the cathedral where several large bells have 
been hung. They are made of a dull, dark metal that looks like 
